{"tid":2031393,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]Google Chrome有用extension","createTime":"2020-05-23T11:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T13:50:43.000Z","uid":86623,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bd96b640e354ce48b599584d3aa0c361fb5b63b3","tid":2031393,"uid":86623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">1. <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/iYiyhKgS5QVCL3kNu-2Xe_V_KCj3BwzPxa1xd7iBvlmGQGm9tBzItUGvz_batLtGmmCodYzkAw=w128-h128-e365\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FiYiyhKgS5QVCL3kNu-2Xe_V_KCj3BwzPxa1xd7iBvlmGQGm9tBzItUGvz_batLtGmmCodYzkAw%3Dw128-h128-e365&h=32e36414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>Google Dictionary (by Google)</ins></div><br />\n睇外語文章, 尤其英文, double-click就可以有簡單嘅字面意義, 做學校網上quiz又幫到手, 由用Chrome用到依家都有用呢個extension<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但留意唔係全部網都用到, 例如連登, 有時work有時唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSetting (right-click extension&gt;option):<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1HP0u2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1HP0u2.png&h=16b655fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2. <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/l1GtA-ghCvZ82Dza_qGtHmSnc2QNyK0AUvX-QCtWS1RsJ87_8nguOTQtR5RGOK6KSbwXNalf=w128-h128-e365\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fl1GtA-ghCvZ82Dza_qGtHmSnc2QNyK0AUvX-QCtWS1RsJ87_8nguOTQtR5RGOK6KSbwXNalf%3Dw128-h128-e365&h=f57d8061&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>uBlock Origin</ins></div><br />\n標榜佢自己係食最少ram同cpu嘅adblocker, 自己用so far冇乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早排都見到有人討論用邊隻adblock for chrome, 留言都係叫各位用uBlock:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1860685/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1860685/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nadblock list (right-click extension&gt;option):<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rsu3kyw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRsu3kyw.png&h=378b6ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W17cYkb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW17cYkb.png&h=1074d3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">3. <img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/oH7Fb165mo1rvlsz2P3yipOI-lDO1_p-8f-MMKi4NDN2AHpfW9cHriBnbX1F23e67jdKUqyo=w128-h128-e365\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FoH7Fb165mo1rvlsz2P3yipOI-lDO1_p-8f-MMKi4NDN2AHpfW9cHriBnbX1F23e67jdKUqyo%3Dw128-h128-e365&h=57d715a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>終結內容農場</ins></div><br />\n顧名思義就係當你打開內容農場時, 佢會進行攔截<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣blogger介紹文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://free.com.tw/content-farm-terminator/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffree.com.tw%2Fcontent-farm-terminator%2F&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSObktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=ee2cf50c\" target=\"_blank\">https://free.com.tw/content-farm-terminator/</a><br />\n<blockquote>根據網友表示<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「封鎖內容農場」實際上是香港使用者開發</span></strong>，黑名單和台灣使用者會上的網站不太一樣，因此如果要作為推廣這款新的「終結內容農場」來說會更具有吸引力，當然我相信功能更完整，也會吸引到越多人使用。</blockquote><br />\n香港人整嘅, 又有用, 必須裝啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網搵資料, 有人建議應該更直接喺個router到set, 但我未試過, 得閒會試下整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n<a href=\"https://stoneip.info/2017/05/12/block-content-farm/99029/front-page/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstoneip.info%2F2017%2F05%2F12%2Fblock-content-farm%2F99029%2Ffront-page%2F&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSObktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=98ad017b\" target=\"_blank\">https://stoneip.info/2017/05/12/block-content-farm/99029/front-page/</a><br />\n<br />\nSetting:<br />\n冇, 即裝即用, 可以自行再加block list<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">4.<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/nBZu0eShu9-2cVafnZsS3XjoIq4PHIYq2s_etN04nE7Sd4i6Ig_ORdGmXP_XiZg-0jOt1vVuLQ=w128-h128-e365\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FnBZu0eShu9-2cVafnZsS3XjoIq4PHIYq2s_etN04nE7Sd4i6Ig_ORdGmXP_XiZg-0jOt1vVuLQ%3Dw128-h128-e365&h=3edeaff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins>HTTPS Everywhere</ins></div><br />\nHTTP<span style=\"color: gold;\">S</span>嘅S, 係代表secure, 所有以HTTPS作網址開頭其實都係有使用到SSL (Secure Sockets Layer) / TLS (Transport Layer Security) , 防止使用者同個website之間傳輸任何資料俾hacker讀取資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但就防唔到狗, 因為狗係唔使hack咁撚on9, 假設你喺連登講咗D嘢引狗, 佢哋係直接申請warrant去搵連仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個extension好處係可以幫你force用https入個website, 變相成個user experience可以更安全<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SxiWFY3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSxiWFY3.png&h=31d7b703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nto<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ucLaLqK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FucLaLqK.png&h=464c8af4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n壞處就有d仍然沿用HTTP嘅網, 係force唔到用HTTPS, 有機會要熄咗個extension先入到<br />\n<br />\nHTTPS詳細解釋:<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.websecurity.digicert.com/zh/hk/security-topics/what-is-ssl-tls-https\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.websecurity.digicert.com%2Fzh%2Fhk%2Fsecurity-topics%2Fwhat-is-ssl-tls-https&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSObktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=144c882f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.websecurity.digicert.com/zh/hk/security-topics/what-is-ssl-tls-https</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\nSetting (left-click extension):<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjcwuS6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjcwuS6.png&h=797b81a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後話:<br />\n本身唔係IT, 只係想分享幾個好用extensions俾各位, 一路用咗好幾年都感覺良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己一掂到人哋部機有chrome就會del晒佢哋d唔等使嘅extension再裝以上四個, 幫埋佢哋set埋, so far d feedback返嚟都係幾好冇投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b917f0486547c00d5cc1afeaa8e5d5a0ad8eeb9d","tid":2031393,"uid":86623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T11:19:11.000Z","msg":"【524前八件事 &mdash;&mdash; 從反送中到反國安法，拜托大家最低限度，要將上年五月尾六月頭做過嘅野，搬返出來做一次。】<br />\n<br />\n一、昨晚紅磡天橋擺聯合站，反應係唔錯既，但記得上年五月尾坐監既時候，每日睇報紙就見到勁多聯署、文宣同埋自發街站遍地開花，既然國安法比起逃犯條例痴線十萬八千倍，家陣疫情將近尾聲，想呼籲大家全民街站，大佬網上大家嗌曬救命，好多人可能仲望住昨日跌既股市，街頭數目真係要多過上年六月九日前。<br />\n<br />\n二、無單張唔知派乜？岑敖暉 Lester Shum同埋八鄉朱凱廸 Chu Hoi Dick昨晚砌左份反國安法單張，再三拜托大家拎去印，唔洗問佢兩個架啦，直接download就得：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WV1C2R；\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WV1C2R%EF%BC%9B&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSObktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=d124bb7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WV1C2R；</a> 另外，乜野貼紙周街貼、海報周圍痴，都好需要文宣手足量產，最好Youtube戰線既朋友都幫手，我地用上年暑假既節奏去應對中共接下來既攻勢。<br />\n<br />\n三、仲有跟開教育議題同埋串連學生既鄭家朗 Isaac Cheng都有同我講，近排教育界同學界清算得咁痴線，查實都會激發大家想做野，咁就麻煩各位校友、家長同埋學生，幫手夾辦學團隊表態；雖然聯署好可能今時今日既作用呢，點都無上年五月尾咁震撼，但至少各校反送中關注組，又係時候郁返，尤其係差唔多考完DSE既學生。<br />\n<br />\n四、去到國際戰線，西方媒體社論發功、美國三大報頭條全撐香港、國會議員排隊相繼表態、國務卿正式發反對，國際關注呢兩日返曬來明顯，我同周庭 Agnes Chow Ting接訪問接足全日無停過，從英美加法德韓日，去到印度土耳其以色列俄羅斯巴基斯坦既記者，都問緊我香港發生乜野事。國際線人人都可以參與！即刻入：<a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSObktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=ec744bee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n四、街頭點搞呢，就大家都明好難畫公仔畫出腸，但我覺得呢個「524遊行前需要解決既四件事」（<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2030135）\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2030135）</a> 寫得非常好，裡面講既幾個問題要傾，而且要盡快聽日前有共識，如果唔係聽日都唔知點好&hellip;&hellip;總之。用唔同方式日間谷人數，至於夜晚就返西方時區一定要用Twitter戰線，呢個週未一定一定一定同國際社會講，香港人會繼續抗爭反擊國安法。<br />\n<br />\n五、無論係「Time is running out in Hong Kong」定係「It is the beginning of the end of Hong Kong」，都係我做訪問時會有既講法，對比起上年都有兩、三個月時間煲起反送中，依家真係極限挑戰，逼香港人未來兩、三星期，從疫情既氣氛，近乎由零開始，唔該大家要將上年五月尾六月頭做過嘅野，搬返出來做一次，仲要做得更好！我地有上年既經驗，應該會谷得更好，快手，盡做。<br />\n<br />\n六、搞成咁，九月選舉有無用？我既答案係：「仲有。」如果仲有投票日既話，無論點DQ，選舉仍然緊要，因為佢確立到國際線同街頭既香港民意基礎同認受性，可能大家身處香港唔覺，但國際一定咁睇。我永遠唔會忘記大學保衛戰炮火連天，唔少記者問我沈默大多數點睇，又話香港人Go Too Far應該反對示威者武力下省五千字&hellip;&hellip;否則會失民心，點知選舉結果贏到開巷，全部質疑批評收曬聲，更唔好講美國總統就係區選大勝三日後簽法案，令《香港人權民主法》 正式生效成為法律；至於制裁，除左若然未報只係時辰未到，大家都明就算制裁鄧炳強凍結西方國家資產，唔代表中共就會立即收回國安法，總之我會盡力同眾志駐華盛頓常委敖卓軒 （Jeffrey Ngo）夾，努力緊。<br />\n<br />\n七、問都唔洗問，全民共識Top Piority，目前最緊要最緊要呢，就一定係要拉倒中共喺香港實施國安法，成數唔高，甚至係低，我知，但上年反送中，大家6月11日，咪一樣有咁既心情，唔係咩？如果睇完以上呢段字，大家都仍然唔太知有咩身位，唔想自己一個做到乜野，歡迎發訊息去羅冠聰 Nathan Law、觀塘願景 - 梁凱晴 Jannelle R. Leung、 張崑陽 Sunny Cheung、何桂藍 Gwyneth Ho既專頁度話想做義工，街站、聯署、文宣、網戰、國際線，大家一定有排忙。<br />\n<br />\n八、最後，想同前日開始 unlike Facebook page，Instagram del相既朋友講，你地洗唔洗驚到咁？驚又好，灰又好，人之常情，我都會擔心，當然有壓力，但洗唔洗去到咁既地步呢&hellip;&hellip;細心諗諗，都知國安法通過之後，頭十個、一百個定甚至一千個清算對像，都無你份架啦，反而我都預左榜上有名，但依家咪又係生勾勾喺香港，打左成篇野比大家睇。唔係講到好有希望，家陣形勢當然差到爆，仲要今鋪國安法，大家都知擺明係要清算國際線，但既然時間無多，就只能兵來將擋，同大家一齊留守香港。<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\n儘管拉人封艇，取締眾志不再是空談，留一口氣，點一盞燈，拜托大家幫忙延續國際戰線血脈：<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E6%87%89%E6%80%A5%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91%E7%B1%8C%E5%8B%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%25B3%2587%25E9%2587%2591%25E7%25B1%258C%25E5%258B%259F%2F&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSObktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=f9787a94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E6%87%89%E6%80%A5%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91%E7%B1%8C%E5%8B%9F/</a><br />\n存亡號召，絕不撤退。<br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/3016279528464535/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200976479994868%2Fposts%2F3016279528464535%2F&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSObktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=252b3978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/3016279528464535/</a>"},{"pid":"d36f69b8af40648eb8f81d9d036abbd881a65c8f","tid":2031393,"uid":50588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"Privacy Badger"},{"pid":"5d7529ed72dd346835c01f6bfe775a7cc0efc5bc","tid":2031393,"uid":78046,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:54:47.000Z","msg":"唔好用chrome 用firefox <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9b700a7b90fb8a7071cfe9ab949a086ed3b374","tid":2031393,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d7529ed72dd346835c01f6bfe775a7cc0efc5bc","tid":2031393,"uid":78046,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:54:47.000Z","msg":"唔好用chrome 用firefox <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"ae88079fe1eae43276804b3ee2c038c4de91a308","tid":2031393,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:39:36.000Z","msg":"有冇播放器介紹"},{"pid":"b2ed93ac13c97589b77c5ebb6a8fdf8e9a46b96e","tid":2031393,"uid":208,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:52:42.000Z","msg":"Brave Browser&lrm; 已經可以取代到2,4<br />\n再唔洗比GOOGLE / FACEBOOK追蹤到你再SELL你廣告<br />\n<br />\n重要係Chrome extension都裝得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://brave.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbrave.com%2F&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSObktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=542edaeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://brave.com/</a>"},{"pid":"045b03319e5eb5b1e7a41aa5ae5ce6e195f94bb1","tid":2031393,"uid":86623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"